  "title": "Routing: support for geosearch",
  "body": "**Do you want to request a *feature* or report a *bug*?**\r\nFeature fix\r\n\r\n**Bug: What is the current behavior?**\r\nThe geosearch connector does not support the new routing API. We should support it.\r\n\r\n**Bug: What is the expected behavior?**\r\nThe map should be in sync with the URL when using the routing.\r\n\r\n**Feature: What is your proposed API entry? The new option to add? What is the behavior?**\r\nTBD @samouss \r\n",
